          <En>A large, long-necked mammal with one or two humps on its back, native to deserts and arid regions, known for its ability to store water and fat.</En>
          <Example>The camel walked steadily across the golden sands of the Sahara.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
